Hello, welcome to the Jeep gearing calculator. Please enter the following when prompted:<br> <br> 
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 1:) The consequent number of each transmission gear ratio when the antecedent equals 1; <br><br>  
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 2:) The consequent number of the transfer case gear ratio selected;<br>  <br> 
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 3) The consequent number of your axle gear ratio when the antecedent equals 1;<br><br>  
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 4) The height (diameter) of your tires in inches; and <br> <br> 
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 5) The road speed in miles per hour you would like to have calculated. <br> <br> 
The page will automatically calculate and display your RPMs at the road speed you input.<br> <br> 
<input type="button" onclick="GRtoRS()" onclick="GRtoRS1()" value="Click" />

